{"tid":975992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（喜訊）香港最低工資終於超越前年既台灣","createTime":"2019-01-10T05:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T08:19:41.000Z","uid":51200,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38296aea18542a8027d50e28c78a9caabdd03386","tid":975992,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"2017年<br />\n國家／地區\t最低工資（港元）<br />\n香港\t34.5/每小時<br />\n台灣\t約35.4/每小時<br />\n中國\t約2,743/每月<br />\n日本\t約57/每小時<br />\n南韓\t約45/每小時<br />\n<br />\n終於超越前年既台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港今年2019貌似加到37.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過上年，<br />\n時薪則從140元（合35.7港元）調至150元（合38.3港元），漲幅7.14％。<br />\n<br />\n台灣2018已經加到38.3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0475087ac1ef23e700c2ddf17f3a3a0d1956cdc7","tid":975992,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45f999d7006477e762101f6be62e8757bd56b7e","tid":975992,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d694804af8f1ffffdf4aa46c919970cc308c0408","tid":975992,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb9796f0463fe898965071a5d3f531811de366a","tid":975992,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飛機打唔成  谷住"},{"pid":"30453dc4d733397ea50748767c06abf150e0c216","tid":975992,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d694804af8f1ffffdf4aa46c919970cc308c0408","tid":975992,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"亞洲國際都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔回歸個水平應該會高過新加坡同日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baeac2716c8de5eeb6a9013f89eab3140640fb4e","tid":975992,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"2019台灣最低工資台幣23k,150/h<br />\n今日匯率計係38.18"},{"pid":"44bbe7836618928e426599280f810c5c2d3dc073","tid":975992,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"其實台灣最低工資咁高，點解大學生人工又咁低"},{"pid":"97e289b6f2afc146a1912735cde635a5c0f30027","tid":975992,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n原來上海北京都有26 27<br />\n廿蚊張真係9up得成既話<br />\n分分鐘香港個最低工資仲低過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於法定最低時薪方面，大陸最高時薪地區是北京的22元人民幣（約27港元），接着是天津20.8元人民幣（約26港元）、上海20元人民幣（約25港元）。在各地區中，最低時薪則在海南地區，只有12.6元人民幣（約16港元）。"},{"pid":"203493a0d8c602aa548b303b1e034fea96f99ab6","tid":975992,"uid":21917,"like":2,"disli